# ── MATLAB binary outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Input .mat files are large binaries — store externally (e.g. SharePoint, DVC)
# Source .m and .mlx files ARE tracked (they are the legacy source code)
MATLAB_Legacy/**/Output Files/
MATLAB_Legacy/**/Output Files/**
*.mat

# ── Simulation outputs (Python) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated result files — reproduce by running the models
*.parquet
*.hdf5
*.h5

# ── Large raw data files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Input Files folders contain raw DoE data — keep local, never push
MATLAB_Legacy/**/Input Files/
MATLAB_Legacy/**/Input Files/**

# ── Temporary & log files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
